'''密葉紅豆杉'''（[[学名|学名]]：''{{lang|la|Taxus fuana}}''）又稱'''喜馬拉雅紅豆杉'''或'''喜馬拉雅密葉紅豆杉'''，是西喜马拉雅地区特有的[[红豆杉属|红豆杉属]]常绿[[乔木|乔木]]<ref>{{cite journal |last1=Poudel |first1=Ram C. |last2=Möller |first2=Michael |last3=Gao |first3=Lian-Ming |last4=Ahrends |first4=Antje |last5=Baral |first5=Sushim R. |last6=Liu |first6=Jie |last7=Thomas |first7=Philip |last8=Li |first8=De-Zhu |title=Using Morphological, Molecular and Climatic Data to Delimitate Yews along the Hindu Kush-Himalaya and Adjacent Regions |journal=PLOS ONE |date=2012-10-08 |volume=7 |issue=10 |pages=e46873 |doi=10.1371/journal.pone.0046873}}</ref>。主要分布于[[阿富汗|阿富汗]]东部沿西喜马拉雅地区至[[中国|中国]][[西藏|西藏]][[吉隆|吉隆]]，以及[[印度|印度]]北部与[[尼泊尔|尼泊尔]]和[[巴基斯坦|巴基斯坦]]<ref>{{cite journal |last1=Song |first1=Yaobin |last2=Xu |first2=Li |last3=Duan |first3=Junpeng |last4=Zhang |first4=Weijun |last5=Shentu |first5=Xiaolu |last6=Li |first6=Tianxiang |last7=Zang |first7=Runguo |last8=Dong |first8=Ming |title=Sex ratio and spatial pattern of Taxus fuana, a Wild Plant with Extremely Small Populations in Tibet |journal=Biodiversity Science |date=2020-03-20 |volume=28 |issue=3 |pages=269 |doi=10.17520/biods.2019102}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal |last1=Deng |first1=Sha |last2=Wu |first2=Yanni |last3=Wu |first3=Kunlin |last4=Fang |first4=Lin |last5=Li |first5=Lin |last6=Zeng |first6=Songjun |title=Breeding characteristics and artificial propagation of 14 species of Wild Plant with Extremely Small Populations (WPESP) in China |journal=Biodiversity Science |date=2020-03-20 |volume=28 |issue=3 |pages=385 |doi=10.17520/biods.2020045}}</ref>。

密葉紅豆杉受到《[[瀕危野生動植物種國際貿易公約|瀕危野生動植物種國際貿易公約]]》附錄二的保護。同时也是中国国家I级重点保护植物。

